mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "The Twenty Basic Movements of Square Dancing", "Stranger in the Land", "The Erie Canal", "Thoughts in General on Square Dancing in Particular", "Do You Know These Square Dancers?", "A Few Tips to Callers of Beginner Classes", and "T.V. Square Dance Pioneers in Australia". This edition also includes the the regular features entitled "Square Dance Date Book", "From the Floor", "As I See It", "Ladies on the Square: Quick Tricks for Christmas Gifts", "Round the Outside Ring", "Caller of the Month: Ernie Gross", "Paging the Roundancers: Bud and Lil Knowland", "What They're Wearing", and "On the Record".
